What’s interesting is it’s with a closed mouth thumbnail (thank gosh open mouth was cringe)  I screamed way less in the video lol  We slowed the video down a lot  Showed more of me and the boys being dumb  cut less than I normally do  And it seems like everyone liked the changes. Hopefully other creators notice because I feel like in general content on YouTube has gotten to fast paced/tense and I want to lead by example and show that viewers don’t want that. Focus less on screaming/moving fast and more on story!
